  "text": "Karabagias et al. reported that thyme did not protect lamb meat in air packaging from oxidation, at least not within its normal shelf life [CITATION_1] . This finding is in contrast to the results of Botsoglou et al. who observed a three-fold reduction in a degree of lipid oxidation in turkey in air packaging [CITATION_2] . ",
